          <p style="font-size:0.93rem;color:var(--muted);margin:0;line-height:1.65;">This is a G3 regulated installation   it cannot be carried out by a general plumber. Our engineers are G3 qualified and carry out all the necessary safety device installation, Building Control notification and commissioning. Unvented cylinder supply and fit from £900 including G3 commissioning certificate. We co-ordinate with loft conversion builders to ensure the cylinder work is timed correctly within the project.</p>
